	<h1 class="title">风云变幻名利场，不是只有女明星才会拼时尚</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Guy Trebay</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-01-10 08:57:57 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/5097/medium/5097.jpg?1436679670" alt="" />			
	</div>
